      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering with this BMW E46 M3. Powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, this example features six individual throttle bodies and a precision 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the Vanos system has been serviced, and the rear subframe\u2014a known structural weak point\u2014has been professionally reinforced. The variable M differential lock ensures optimal torque distribution, while the factory suspension maintains its signature communicative feedback and cornering poise. This is a mechanically sound, driver-focused machine ready for the canyons. Comprehensive maintenance records and a clean title are included.",
